OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering 'dedicated and
OL,4,Cloving' grandad, 72, in his home
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of the
OL,7,Fmurder of a pensioner, who was found
OL,8,Fdead in his home with stab wounds and
OL,9,Fassault injuries.
OL,11,FSukhkit Bains, 46, stabbed his
OL,12,Facquaintance Michael Martin, 72, in a
OL,13,Fsustained attack inside his home in St
OL,14,FBotolph's Road in March.
OL,16,FThe court heard how Mr Martin had been
OL,17,Ffound by a family member at his
OL,18,Faddress on 22 March this year.
