OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering 'dedicated and
OL,4,Cloving' grandad, 72, in his home
OL,6,FBains had made efforts to conceal his
OL,7,Fcrime inside the address, including
OL,8,Fwiping clean a knife, turning over a
OL,9,Fblood-stained rug, and putting his own
OL,10,Fblood-stained clothing in the washing
OL,11,Fmachine.
OL,13,FHe was later arrested in Crawley and
OL,14,Fcharged with murder.
OL,16,FSukhjit Bains, of Southgate, stood
OL,17,Ftrial at Isleworth Crown Court, where
OL,18,Fhe was found guilty of murder by the
OL,19,Fjury.
