OL,6,FIn a statement following the verdict,
OL,7,FMr Martin's family said he was a
OL,8,Floving and dedicated dad and grandad.
OL,10,FThey said: "He always had time for
OL,11,Fpeople, found solace in making
OL,12,Ffriends, and would do anything to help
OL,13,Fanyone.
OL,15,F"We had the best dad in the world. He
OL,16,Fwas our hero and he taught us to love,
OL,17,Fto be kind, and to always look after
OL,18,Feach other.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
