OL,6,F"There are simply no words to describe
OL,7,Fthe level of pain and loss we continue
OL,8,Fto feel."
OL,10,FThey said the crime has left them to
OL,11,Fnavigate "immense feelings of
OL,12,Fdevastation and grief".
OL,14,FThe family added: "Our dad met a
OL,15,Fviolent predator that preyed on the
OL,16,Fvulnerable. He has taken away the last
OL,17,Fprecious years we had with our dad and
OL,18,Fgrandad.
OL,20,F"This act is something we will never
OL,21,Fbe able to comprehend or forgive."
