OL,6,FDetective Inspector Amanda Zinyama
OL,7,Ffrom the Surrey and Sussex Major Crime
OL,8,FTeam said: "This was a distressing
OL,9,Fcase, and our thoughts continue to be
OL,10,Fwith the family and loved-ones of Mr
OL,11,FMartin.
OL,13,F"Bains carried out a sustained and
OL,14,Fviolent attack upon him in his home.
OL,16,F"We were determined to get answers for
OL,17,FMr Martin's family and to ensure that
OL,18,FBains was brought to justice.
