OL,6,F"I would like to say thank you to the
OL,7,Fwitnesses who have come forward and to
OL,8,Fthe public for supporting our complex
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,F"We are pleased that the jury has
OL,12,Ffound Bains guilty of this crime, and
OL,13,Fhe now faces sentencing."
OL,15,FBains now faces sentencing at
OL,16,FIsleworth Crown Court on 1 November.
